name: Zombie Warhol Black Wood Frame
description:
Andy Warhol always had this incredibly dapper look no matter where he went and always appeared ready for the camera. I can't help but imagine that even if he came back from the dead as a walking corpse that he would still be rocking his wig and looking as stylish as always

Zombie Warhol Black Wood Frames will initially be limited at 75 editions. All editions will be offered for free on Hicetnunc. After 24 hours of the initial sale going public, the remaining editions will be burned.
